('Alexander W.', 'Alexander', 'W.', 'General Manager at Amari (Onyx Hospitality Group)', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/alexanderwillmann', 'alexanderwillmann', $${"about": "With over a decade of international experience in luxury hospitality, I currently serve as General Manager at Amari Koh Samui. My focus is on fostering a people-centric, accountability-driven culture that prioritizes engagement, leadership visibility, and talent development. By aligning the right team members with the right roles, we aim to deliver enhanced performance, cultivate cultural consistency, and elevate the guest experience to create emotion-led and memorable moments.  \n\nMy expertise lies in resort development, food and beverage operations, and customer support. Drawing on experience from global destinations, I bring a deep understanding of cultural nuances and a commitment to operational excellence. At Amari Koh Samui, my mission is to strengthen team culture and deliver outstanding guest experiences that celebrate the unique charm of the island, while embodying the warmth and authenticity of the ONYX Hospitality Group ethos.", "addressCountryOnly": "Thailand", "addressWithCountry": "Thailand, Thailand", "addressWithoutCountry": "Thailand", "backgroundPic": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5616AQFvWaFvAwGpDQ/profile-displaybackgroundimage-shrink_350_1400/B56ZcwIl5iHgAY-/0/1748859249478?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=WaQCNcZjPyhjldC1ayMxOaF0QQJOP4ZRbZuNj59yZL4", "companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "companyLinkedin": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/onyx-hospitality-group/", "companyName": "ONYX Hospitality Group", "companySize": "1001-5000", "companyWebsite": "http://www.onyx-hospitality.com/", "connections": "1190", "currentJobDuration": "11 mos", "currentJobDurationInYrs": "0.92", "educations/0/companyId": "18946", "educations/0/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/school/cornell-university/", "educations/0/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:18946", "educations/0/description": "Marketi