ri Dhaka Hotel; in charge of all hotel operations as well as the the Breeze spa, Fitness center, and Deck 41 the new night club/restaurant over looking the city.  Amari a 5 star Hotel right at the heart of the diplomatic zone in Dhaka which hosts some of the most prestigious and honorable events in Bangladesh.  The hotel has 134 Deluxe rooms and suites, Breeze spa, new Fit-Centre over looking the city and 5 Food and Beverage outlets.  Sense opening have taken the hotel to an average annual occupancy of 68% and running over budget YTD.  Currently have an average GOP of 50.06% and GOP retention over 100%;  total revenue up 22% YOY.  Running Sales and Marketing as well doing dual roles for the last 14 months running REVPAR of 7.45% over budget and number 2/3 in our comp set month to month.  Winner of GM of the Year for hospitality 2019.", "experiences/2/jobEndedOn": "1-2020", "experiences/2/jobLocation": "Dhaka, Bangladesh", "experiences/2/jobLocationCountry": "TH", "experiences/2/jobStartedOn": "1-2015", "experiences/2/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/2/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D560BAQHF9E51LyeHpQ/company-logo_400_400/B56Zvpil52IYAY-/0/1769149718610/onyx_hospitality_group_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=DvS3pLIilWUhrkh8a9yBT0QnCRF2VHXKRgekG6R4CdU", "experiences/2/title": "General Manager of Amari Dhaka", "experiences/3/companyId": "73878", "experiences/3/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/3/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/dusit-hotels-and-resorts/", "experiences/3/companyName": "Dusit International, dusitD2 Phuket Resort", "experiences/3/companySize": "5001-10000", "experiences/3/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:73878", "experiences/3/companyWebsite": "http://www.dusit.com", "experiences/3/jobDescription": "General Manager of the dusitD2 Phuket Resort, a premium hotel featuring  newly renovated rooms and suites on Phuket island, located in Patong Beach. The dusitD2 Phuket Resort features 390 guestrooms,one large swimming pool in the centre of the resort, a rooftop swimming pool with a bar offering stunning views over the sea, The Hard Rock Café, the only Hooters in Thailand and one of the best Kids clubs in Asia as well as Siam Adventure Club.  The completion of D-Bar in the lobby will simply amaze you it is simply a piece of art.", "experiences/3/jobEndedOn": "3-2015", "experiences/3/jobLocation": "Patong, Thailand", "experiences/3/jobLocationCountry": "TH", "experiences/3/jobStartedOn": "5-2014", "experiences/3/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/3/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D560BAQGWMHIk9QEgDw/company-logo_400_400/B56ZoZPoypJQAY-/0/1761360122041/dusit_hotels_and_resorts_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=FLJ8WBd5R9JloKB_DRhwqZyBPeZ9Snnh_2Lf31yw6XQ", "experiences/3/title": "General Manager", "experiences/4/companyName": "Indigo Pearl Phuket (Currently rebranded to \"The Slate\")", "experiences/4/jobDescription": "General Manager of the Indigo Pearl Resort; located on Nai Yang Beach on Phuket’s northwest shore, expanding to the Andaman Sea. Indigo Pearl Resort includes 219 Suites, 7 Villas and 35 Pool Pavilions, 8 Food & Beverage Outlets, 3 Swimming Pools and Pool Bars, Coqoon Spa winner of the \"Best Luxury Resort Spa award\" with newly renovated Fitness Center, Newly designed Bill Bensley meeting space and new Night Club and Retail Boutiques, managing over 500 staff.  Phuket's most Distinctive Resort and the most recent recipient of the \"Best Luxury Beach Resort award\" in Thailand, as well as the 2013 recipient of Best Luxury Design Resort in Asia. Host of the World luxury resort awards dinner and ceremony that we received the highest honor \"Best Luxury Suite and Villa Resort in the World\". YOY financial results up 22%, ADR increase of 18%, more details upon request.", "experiences/4/jobEndedOn": "4-2014", "experiences/4/jobLocation": "Phuket, Thailand", "experiences/4/jobStartedOn": "7-2011", "experiences/4/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/4/title": "